#: ../../docs/technical/use-cases.rst:164
msgid ""
"When in doubt, start with HStore. It's simpler, more compact, and gives "
"you a better admin experience. Migrate to JSONB only when you genuinely "
"need nested structures or mixed value types."
msgstr ""
"সন্দেহ থাকলে HStore দিয়ে শুরু করুন। এটি সিম্পল, বেশি compact, এবং "
"বেশি ভালো admin experience দেয়। শুধুমাত্র nested structures বা mixed value "
"types সত্যিই লাগলে JSONB-তে migrate করুন।"
